   :evidence ["cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-paged-cache-summary.md"]}
  {:id :recompute-negative
   :statement "Whole-prefix recompute each token increases peak device memory"
   :evidence ["benchmarks/sqrt-kv-mac-m4-validation.md"]}
  {:id :decode-cost
   :statement "Re-paging every decode step is 2.2x-3.7x slower than full-KV decode, cross-validated by two independent measurement methods, worsening with S"
   :evidence ["cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-throughput-modal-summary.md"
              "cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-paged-cache-summary.md"]}
  {:id :competitive-comparison
   :statement "At ~90% compression matching this method's own headline numbers, kvpress's StreamingLLM/Knorm/SnapKV score 0% needle-retrieval accuracy; sqrt(S) residency is exact by construction"
   :evidence ["cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-kvpress-summary.md"]}
  {:id :mla-composability-gap
   :statement "Neither the HuggingFace nor the mlx-lm reference implementation of DeepSeek-V2 caches the MLA-compressed latent; true composability with an absorbed-cache implementation remains open"
   :evidence ["cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-mla-summary.md"
              "cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-mac-mla-source-inspection.md"]}
  {:id :unified-memory-mechanism
   :statement "On Apple Silicon unified memory, naive host offload (write+del) does not free real RSS; np.memmap-based paging does, confirmed to 0.0MB RSS cost up to 6.3GB non-resident"
   :evidence ["cloud-murakumo docs/benchmarks/sqrt-kv-mac-memory-capability-summary.md"]}
  {:id :capability-unlock
   :statement "GLM-4-9B-Chat-1M (native 1,048,576-token context) reaches only 6.1%/24.8% of native context on 16GB/32GB Mac without this technique; real measured bpt + weight size, not estimated"
